'''WikiBaseball''' ({{zh|t=臺灣棒球維基館}}) is a [[Taiwan]]ese [[baseball]] website. It was created on April 14, 2005.<ref name="launch date"/> Its major contents are people, event, time, place, and merchandise of Taiwanese baseball.
Wikibaseball runs on [[MediaWiki]] software. It is written collaboratively by volunteers. Besides [[feature story]], all content is available under [[Creative Commons|CC-BY-NC]].<ref name="licenses">{{cite web |url=http://twbsball.dils.tku.edu.tw/wiki/index.php/TwBsBall:%E7%89%88%E6%AC%8A%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF |title=TwBsBall:版權信息 |accessdate=2007-03-31 |publisher=Wikibaseball |language= Chinese }}</ref>
Because many people browse this website. [[United Daily News]], [[Formosa Television]] and some Taiwan [[Mass media|media]] introduce this website to [[Taiwanese people]] on March 2006.<ref name="UDN">{{cite news |script-title=zh:想看台灣棒球瘋 網站全都錄 |url=http://ndap.dils.tku.edu.tw:8080/ndap/querynews2.jsp?id=218383 |publisher=台灣棒球運動珍貴新聞檔案數位資料館 |date=2006-03-09 |accessdate=2007-04-01 |language= Chinese }}</ref>[http://ndap.dils.tku.edu.tw/site/tv/]{{Dead link|date=September 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} After several month, Wikibaseball teamed up with [[Chinese Taipei Baseball Association]] to digitize their relic. In addition, two Wikibaseball contributors contributed to [[Liberty Times]] and interviewed by [[Uonline]] reporter on March 2007.<ref name="contribute">{{cite news |script-title=zh:棒球？ 來寫吧！ |url=http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2007/new/mar/4/today-o10.htm |publisher=[[Liberty Times]] |date=2007-03-04 |accessdate=2007-04-01 |language= Chinese }}</ref><ref name="interview">{{cite news |script-title=zh:楊子逸編撰維基台灣棒球史 |url=http://www.uonline.nccu.edu.tw/content_text.asp?ano=222 |publisher=[[Uonline]] |date=2007-03-15 |accessdate=2007-04-01 |language= Chinese }} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>
